{"tid":1615983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（好重要有片）沙嘴道同龍翔道十五米外距離瞄向示威者開三槍，不過好彩唔中","createTime":"2019-10-03T09:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T15:40:44.000Z","uid":294761,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ba32abbd1143b2e4c5ac941c1a70526c8c7465da","tid":1615983,"uid":294761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://streamable.com/mj1r0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fmj1r0&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=df3141f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/mj1r0</a><br />\n<br />\n除左荃灣近距離開槍謀殺同油麻地向天開槍外，<br />\n沙嘴道同龍翔道開呢三槍點解冇人講，記者又冇報？<br />\n只有一槍比人影到係九丈遠平射示威者，係警察冇生命威脅下意圖搵示威者練靶啊！！<br />\n唔該勇武你地真係唔好以為衝埋去打先有事啊，呢三槍唔中真係好彩咋，向住咁多target射埋去，好大機會會中一個！<br />\n我真係唔想見到你地出事，暫時冇其他更有效嘅武器之前希望大家忍一忍，唔好面對面去攻擊黑警，其他做咩都支持！"},{"pid":"623734bf82e5220299c9740d66d2812a2378338d","tid":1615983,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6cdd66fb01354952eaa05000aea5d8aa1bff45","tid":1615983,"uid":258748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:16:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49f781bb4751dc18bc52e71da659b1b32aa1255","tid":1615983,"uid":31151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"其實呢單仲大獲"},{"pid":"6362f056d0c23972e13782a9debf3b1d519ae0c7","tid":1615983,"uid":294761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a49f781bb4751dc18bc52e71da659b1b32aa1255","tid":1615983,"uid":31151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"其實呢單仲大獲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"First aid 同記者都好危險"},{"pid":"86e653734cfa6561740237a8bbc1605a7f37dd4d","tid